sequenceDiagram
    actor Guest
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as Elysia API
    participant Redis
    participant Worker
    participant Whisper
    participant Ollama
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    actor Staff

    Guest->>FE: Records voice (any language)
    FE->>API: POST /api/requests/voice
    API->>PG: INSERT request (queued)
    API->>Redis: Enqueue → transcription
    API-->>FE: { request_id }
    FE->>API: Opens SSE stream

    Redis->>Worker: Dequeue transcription
    Worker->>Whisper: POST /transcribe
    Whisper-->>Worker: { text, lang, confidence }
    Worker->>PG: INSERT transcription
    Worker->>Redis: Publish status update
    API-->>FE: "Transcribed ✓"

    Worker->>Redis: Enqueue → classification
    Redis->>Worker: Dequeue classification
    Worker->>Ollama: POST /api/generate
    Ollama-->>Worker: { department, urgency, summary }
    Worker->>PG: INSERT classification + workflow
    Worker->>Redis: Publish to staff channels
    API-->>FE: "Routed to Maintenance ✓"

    Redis-->>API: Pub/sub event
    API->>Staff: WebSocket push (new workflow card)
    Staff->>API: POST /workflows/:id/claim
    API->>Redis: Publish update
    API-->>FE: "Juan is on the way"
